        "subject": "LU-5956 o2iblnd: wrong uses of kib_tx_t::tx_nfrags",
        "message": "LU-5956 o2iblnd: wrong uses of kib_tx_t::tx_nfrags\n\nThe kib_tx_t::tx_nfrags field is the # entries in\nthe kib_tx_t::tx_frags array, rather than # DMA\nmapped entries. So kiblnd_send/kiblnd_recv should\nuse kib_rdma_desc_t::rd_nfrags instead.\n\nSigned-off-by: Doug Oucharek <doug.s.oucharek@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I035bbfdcc9b416b450164d91c5fd179ee1eff92b\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b1_8"
    }
